The way you are trying to set environment variables is not persistent between Ansible tasks. You should use the `environment` directive, either at a task or a play level. 

For example (task level):
```
- name: install mongodb python bindings via pip
  pip: name=pymongo version=&quot;{{mongodb_version}}&quot;
  environment:
    http_proxy: &quot;{{ http_proxy }}&quot;
    https_proxy: &quot;{{ https_proxy }}&quot;
```
Or (play level):
```
- hosts: all
  environment:
    http_proxy: &quot;{{ http_proxy }}&quot;
    https_proxy: &quot;{{ https_proxy }}&quot;
```

